data.description: Beautiful and peaceful property available on one and a half acres with big mature hardwoods in front yard. Popular & sought after location close to town and only minutes to Tims Ford Lake. All brick home with a detached garage concrete floor, spacious backyard with a newly built porch & fully fenced. Two small paddocks for livestock with a shelter. Dishwasher, microwave, refrigerator, and stove are new!
